# Product API – Node.js, MongoDB, Redis, PM2

## Overview

This project is a high-performance Product API built using Node.js and Express.
It demonstrates industry-level backend practices including database indexing, Redis caching, and horizontal scaling using PM2 cluster mode.

The API retrieves product data from MongoDB and caches responses in Redis to reduce database load and improve response times.

---

## Tech Stack

* Node.js
* Express.js
* MongoDB
* Mongoose
* Redis (Caching Layer)
* PM2 (Process Manager & Clustering)

---

## Features

* REST API for product retrieval
* Redis caching for faster responses
* MongoDB indexing for optimized queries
* PM2 cluster mode for multi-core scalability
* Modular project structure
* Error handling and logging

---

